          기차, 버스, 비행기, 특히 그 소리에 대한 깊은 관심
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group p-5 rounded-xl bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-900/70 backdrop-blur-sm border border-red-200/50 dark:border-red-800/50 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105"
      >
        <div
          class="text-3xl mb-3 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-6"
        >
          🎮
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 mb-2">게임</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Cities: Skylines, Geoguessr
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group p-5 rounded-xl bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-900/70 backdrop-blur-sm border border-fuchsia-200/50 dark:border-fuchsia-800/50 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105"
